OL,4,CFree school meals: Poorer pupils miss
OL,5,Cout in funding change, say unions
OL,6, A "worrying" number of poorer school
OL,7, pupils will miss out on extra funding
OL,8, because of a change in the way support
OL,9, is allocated, unions say.
OL,11,FNew figures show more than one in five
OL,12,Fchildren in England are now eligible
OL,13,Ffor free school meals - an increase of
OL,14,F420,000 children since March 2020.
OL,16,FBut extra funding for schools will be
OL,17,Fbased on data from last October rather
OL,18,Fthan the latest figures for January.
OL,20,FThe government says the date change
OL,21,Fwill help with budget planning.
